contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:48.550 --> 02:52.730
A 1987 Foothill High
School yearbook,of course.

02:53.930 --> 02:56.450
How about th-the ghetto blaster?

02:58.230 --> 02:59.890
Rubik's Cube?

03:00.820 --> 03:01.850
How about this?

03:01.890 --> 03:03.480
CD,no needle required.

03:03.500 --> 03:07.590
In 20 years,they'll be able to put
hundreds of those on a microchip.

03:07.600 --> 03:10.310
Victim had several ante-mortem
fractures to his sternum,

03:10.340 --> 03:14.460
as well as several antemortem fractures
to the lateral sections of his ribs.

03:14.480 --> 03:15.620
All healed?

03:15.630 --> 03:17.830
All healed at different times.

03:17.880 --> 03:19.840
I had a Michael Jackson glove.

03:19.870 --> 03:21.280
I've never mentioned that before.

03:21.310 --> 03:23.010
I loved Chevy Chase.

03:23.030 --> 03:24.350
We all have our crosses to bear.

03:24.380 --> 03:27.870
The fracture on the
right clavicle is fresh.

03:27.910 --> 03:30.080
Well,was,20 years ago.

03:30.100 --> 03:32.610
Oh! Mullet alert!

03:32.650 --> 03:34.760
Ooh,that's a nasty one.

03:34.780 --> 03:37.660
Booth got a list of all the students who
didn't make it to the capsule opening,

03:37.680 --> 03:42.430
and he's pulling the names of anyone connected
to the school in 1987 who had a record.

03:42.470 --> 03:47.620
Oh,my God,I'm getting flashbacks
to braces and stirrup pants

03:47.630 --> 03:50.380
and a really,really bad side ponytail.

03:50.400 --> 03:51.500
You certainly grew out of it.

03:51.530 --> 03:54.120
I wore Doc Marten's that
weighed more than I did.

03:54.130 --> 03:55.780
Apparently Booth was fine.

03:55.820 --> 03:56.980
He was a football player.

03:56.990 --> 03:59.840
Right. He was one ofthoseguys.

03:59.870 --> 04:03.130
Well,this guy certainly wasn't
hanging out with the cheerleaders,

04:03.160 --> 04:07.820
but I bet he had some love notes
stashed away in hisSpaceballs binder.

04:07.870 --> 04:09.570
I think I saw him in the video.

04:09.590 --> 04:11.140
Roger Dillon.

04:12.420 --> 04:14.380
Class of 1987.

04:14.400 --> 04:15.220
Here he is.

04:15.250 --> 04:17.050
The comet will be around in 76 years.

04:17.079 --> 04:18.880
We'll still be around,don't worry.

04:20.950 --> 04:25.160
How did Roger Dillon get fromthere...

04:26.500 --> 04:28.440
to here?

